NOTE:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Horizontal Split:	(Ctrl)+(b)+(+)
Vertical Split:		(Ctrl)+(b)+(-)
Enable Scrolling:	(Ctrl)+(b)+([)
Disable Scrolling:	(Esc)
Status Bar On/Off:	(Ctrl)+(b)+(b)
Man Page In New Window:	(Ctrl)+(b)+(m) + <keyword to rearch> + (Enter)
				e.g.: (Ctrl)+(b)+(m) + <wget> + (Enter)
Move Around Windows:	(Ctrl)+(b)+(arrows)
			(Ctrl)+(b)+(vim style "h,j,k,l")
Resize Windows:		(Ctrl)+(b)+(arrows) !Without leaving Ctrl!
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

cp tmux.conf ~/.tmux.conf
